node.text:
Cajun spiced roasted veggies served over buttery chive grits and topped with a creamy, spicy southern inspired sauce! Recipe at:

https://www.rabbitandwolves.com/vegan-creamy-southern-roasted-vegetables/
Or click the link in my profile @rabbitandwolves 
#vegan #veganrecipes #veganfood #plantbased
